---
<Base
  title="Logos — Portafolio de Identidad Visual · Marcos Santiago"
  description="Más de 50 identidades visuales diseñadas por Marcos Santiago — branding, logos y sistemas de diseño desde Puerto Rico."
  image="/shorts-og.jpg"
>
  <Nav />

  <section class="logos-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="logos-label">Identidad Visual</p>
      <h1 class="logos-title">LOGOS</h1>
      <p class="logos-sub">{logos.length} marcas diseñadas desde Puerto Rico</p>
      <button class="bg-toggle" id="bgToggle">
        <span class="bg-toggle-icon" id="bgToggleIcon">☀️</span>
        <span id="bgToggleText">Ver en fondo blanco</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    const btn = document.getElementById('bgToggle');
    const icon = document.getElementById('bgToggleIcon');
    const text = document.getElementById('bgToggleText');
    btn?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const isLight = document.documentElement.dataset.theme === 'light';
      document.documentElement.dataset.theme = isLight ? 'dark' : 'light';
      localStorage.setItem('ms-theme', isLight ? 'dark' : 'light');
      icon!.textContent = isLight ? '☀️' : '🌙';
      text!.textContent = isLight ? 'Ver en fondo blanco' : 'Ver en fondo oscuro';
    });
    // Set initial state
    const current = document.documentElement.dataset.theme;
    if (current === 'light') {
      icon!.textContent = '🌙';
      text!.textContent = 'Ver en fondo oscuro';
    }
  </script>

  <section class="logos-section">
    <div class="logos-grid">
      {logos.map(l => (
        <div class="logo-card">
          <div class="logo-card-inner">
            <img src={`/logos-portfolio/${l.file}`} alt={l.name} class="logo-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <span class="logo-name">{l.name}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fase1-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="fase1-card">
        <div class="fase1-copy">
          <p class="fase1-label">Colaboración</p>
          <h2 class="fase1-title">Fase1</h2>
          <p class="fase1-desc">Estos logos fueron creados en colaboración con <a href="https://fase1.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="fase1-link">Fase1</a>, un programa virtual gratuito que ayuda a emprendedores a convertir sus ideas en negocios exitosos. Cada identidad visual fue diseñada para darle a estas marcas emergentes una presencia profesional desde el primer día.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://fase1.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="fase1-btn">
          Conoce Fase1 →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
/* ── Hero ── */
.logos-hero {
  padding: 140px 0 64px;
  text-align: center;
}
.logos-label {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .65rem;
  letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.logos-title {
  font-family: var(--display);
  font-size: clamp(5rem, 18vw, 14rem);
  letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: .88;
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.logos-sub {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .7rem;
  letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
}

/* ── BG Toggle ── */
.bg-toggle {
  margin-top: 28px;
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 999px;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: #08080c;
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .75rem;
  letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700;
  border: none; cursor: pointer;
  transition: transform .15s, box-shadow .15s;
  box-shadow: 0 0 32px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 40%, transparent);
}
.bg-toggle:hover {
  transform: scale(1.04);
  box-shadow: 0 0 48px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 60%, transparent);
}
.bg-toggle-icon { font-size: 1rem }

/* ── Grid ── */
.logos-section {
  padding: 0 0 100px;
}
.logos-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
  gap: 1px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
}

/* ── Card ── */
.logo-card {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  gap: 14px;
  padding: 40px 28px 28px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  transition: background .2s;
  cursor: default;
}
.logo-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 5%, transparent);
  opacity: 0; transition: opacity .2s;
}
.logo-card:hover::before { opacity: 1 }

.logo-card-inner {
  height: 64px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  width: 100%;
}
.logo-img {
  max-height: 64px; max-width: 100%; width: auto;
  opacity: .8;
  transition: opacity .2s;
  object-fit: contain;
}
.logo-card:hover .logo-img { opacity: 1 }

.logo-name {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .58rem;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted); text-align: center;
  transition: color .2s;
}
.logo-card:hover .logo-name { color: var(--accent) }

/* ── Fase1 ── */
.fase1-section {
  padding: 80px 0 100px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.fase1-card {
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between; gap: 40px;
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px; padding: 40px 48px;
}
.fase1-label {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .62rem;
  letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.fase1-title {
  font-family: var(--display); font-size: 2.8rem;
  letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.fase1-desc {
  font-size: var(--text-base); color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.7; max-width: 60ch;
}
.fase1-link {
  color: var(--accent); text-decoration: underline;
  text-underline-offset: 3px;
}
.fase1-btn {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .68rem;
  letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 45%, transparent);
  color: var(--accent);
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 8%, transparent);
  transition: .2s ease; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.fase1-btn:hover {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 16%, transparent);
  border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 70%, transparent);
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .fase1-card { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; padding: 28px 24px }
}

/* ── Mobile ── */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .logos-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr) }
  .logo-card { padding: 28px 16px 20px }
  .logo-card-inner { height: 48px }
  .logo-img { max-height: 48px }
}
</style>
